data.description: Do not let this investment opportunity slip through your fingers. Act now to turbocharge your investment portfolio today! Calling all visionaries and DIY enthusiasts! This is your ultimate chance to transform this house into your dream home. With four bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a convenient half bathroom stubbed in bedroom 4, this property is a perfect canvas for your creative ideas. Inside, you'll find a formal living room and dining room for gatherings, a kitchen with plenty of cabinets, and a cozy family room with a fireplace. The spacious rooms offer endless customization possibilities, allowing you to design each space to match your style. Outside, the potential continues with landscaping and personal touches to create your own outdoor retreat with an inground pool. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to craft a home that reflects your personality. Schedule a showing today and kickstart your renovation journey!
